title: Northland Bank
description:
Welcome to the Northland Bank. So traveler, do you wish to join the Fatui?
Here are some things you can do as soon as you hop in!
• Genshin talk? We have the chatters just for you.
• Explore our art gallery and view tons of amazing duly credited fan arts.
• Be updated with the latest leaks from lots of reliable people.
• A good story makes a good game. Join in on our lore discussions!
• Anything to brag about? Or maybe something to cry about? Our flex channel might be to your liking.
